Physics Informed Neural Network

Forward Problem: 1D Heat Equation and Viscous Burgers Equation

Structure:
PINN/
в”ңв”Җв”Җ README
в”ңв”Җв”Җ .gitignore
в”ңв”Җв”Җ ckpt.pt # latest Adam-phase checkpoint (overwritten each run)
в”ңв”Җв”Җ src/
в”Ӯ в”ңв”Җв”Җ model.py # PINN class (nn.Module)
в”Ӯ в”ңв”Җв”Җ physics.py # PDE residual, BC/IC functions
в”Ӯ в”ңв”Җв”Җ train.py # training loop, Adam + L-BFGS
в”Ӯ в”ңв”Җв”Җ sampling.py # collocation point generation
в”Ӯ в”ңв”Җв”Җ eval.py # error metrics
в”Ӯ в”ңв”Җв”Җ plot.py # plotting helpers
в”Ӯ в”ңв”Җв”Җ run*experiments.py # runs all 8 Python experiments, generates all_plots/
в”Ӯ в””в”Җв”Җ plot_cpp_experiments.py # generates all C++ graphs into all_plots/
в”ңв”Җв”Җ py_logs/ # Python run logs
в”Ӯ в”ңв”Җв”Җ evals.csv
в”Ӯ в”ңв”Җв”Җ experiment_manifest.json
в”Ӯ в””в”Җв”Җ perf*<name>_<time>.csv # per-epoch timing (8 files)
в”ңв”Җв”Җ py_runs/ # Python model checkpoints (.pt)
в”ңв”Җв”Җ all_plots/
в”Ӯ в”ңв”Җв”Җ py_experiments/ # Python experiment graphs
в”Ӯ в”Ӯ в”ңв”Җв”Җ <name>\_loss_curves.png
в”Ӯ в”Ӯ в”ңв”Җв”Җ heat_errors.png
в”Ӯ в”Ӯ в””в”Җв”Җ burgers_errors.png
в”Ӯ в””в”Җв”Җ cpp_experiments/ # C++ experiment graphs
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ <name>\_loss_curves.png # requires C++ rebuild + re-run, didn't have time to create
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ heat_errors.png
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ burgers_errors.png
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ <name>\_timing.png # 8 per-epoch timing graphs
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ timing_comparison_py_vs_cpp.png
в”ңв”Җв”Җ plots1/ - plots6/ # historical single-run plots (loss curves, heatmaps)
в”ңв”Җв”Җ cpp/ # C++ port (LibTorch)
